==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Empassion
<hw>Em*pas"sion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To move with
passion; to affect strongly. See <er>Impassion</er>.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Those sights <qex>empassion</qex> me full near.</q>
<rj><qau>Spenser.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Empassionate</ent>⟦br⟧
